p: ['Gurgaon is the destination of choice for the real estate investors in India. Till around two decades ago Gurgaon was just another economical wasteland. However liberalization of the economy and the coming up of the outsourcing industry opened the floodgates of growth giving rise to an affluent middle-class with purchasing power in their hands and dreams for a good life in their hearts.', 'Gurgaon became and is today one of the most promising destination to invest in. There are several factors that go in favor of Gurgaon. ', 'First Gurgaon is part of the national capital region of Delhi and is well-connected with the capital via the metro NH8 and Mehrauli Gurgaon Road. The Dwarka Expressway which is currently under construction will further improve connectivity by road.', 'Gurgaon is well connected to the rest of the country and the world via the Indira Gandhi International Airport.', 'As there was shortage of space in Delhi it was natural for expansion to happen in the neighboring Gurgaon. Multinationals business houses Fortune 500 companies that were looking to expand and wanted space to house their ever-growing workforce set shop in Gurgaon. This gave rise to a high demand for real estate property including both residential and commercial property. Today all real estate developers worth their name have their projects in Gurgaon. While there are several ready to move in project in the city there are also new projects in Gurgaon for those who initially missed the bus.', 'When it comes to buying property location makes all the difference. While there are projects coming up in most parts of the city some of the more favorable new projects in Gurgaon can be found near the Dwarka Expressway. ', 'If you are looking to invest in new projects in Gurgaon you can consider residential and commercial property options in sector 109 near the Dwarka Expressway. ', 'Take the case of Lumbini Terrace Homes a residential complex being developed by Brisk Infrastructure and Developers. The residential complex consist of high-rise towers with 2 bhk 3 bhk and 4 bhk apartments. ', 'If you are on a budget or a small family you can book 2 bhk apartments in new residential projects in Gurgaon. If you are more flexible with the budget or looking for more space 3 bhk and 4 bhk apartments will be more suited to your purpose. ', 'If you buy a residential apartment in any of the new projects in Gurgaon you will benefit in several ways. To explain them let us again consider residential apartments available for sale in Lumbini Terrace Homes. ', 'Whether you are interested in a 2 bhk 3 bhk and 4 bhk apartment you will find that all these apartment types are spacious and boast an intelligent use of layout and design. For instance all apartments have large balconies overlooking beautifully landscaped gardens. And if you buy an apartments in the higher stories you can also gain a birds eye view of the city. The new projects in Gurgaon are a haven of peace and tranquility and put you away from the madding pace of the city. At the same time they offer great connectivity to the rest of the city so you can easily reach your office within a few minutes. Similarly the shopping malls which Gurgaon is famous for world-class restaurants bars and other entertainment facilities are within convenient driving distance. So these new projects in Gurgaon give you the best of both the worlds  an oasis of peace and tranquility within their gated complex and easy connectivity to the rest of the city.', 'The new projects in Gurgaon are being designed to give you the best of privacy and access to a range of shared amenities. For instance new projects in Gurgaon such as Lumbini Terrace Homes has a swimming pool common areas for children to play recreational areas for adults landscaped gardens for socializing and early morning or late evening walks. Besides the new projects in Gurgaon also provide 24 hour security water supply and power backup. With all the necessities taken care of you will be relieved of much of your stress and have time at your hands to spend on yourself your family or your friends.', 'Whether you are an investor or a buyer purchasing property in new projects in Gurgaon will yield better return on investment. For one the apartments in new projects in Gurgaon are considerably cheaper than ready to move in flats in existing projects. So if you are willing to wait buying property in new projects in Gurgaon will be a good option to invest.', 'If you wish to invest in new projects in Gurgaon you can consider investing during the pre-launch an soft-launch phases of the project development. During these phases you can benefit from further discounts given the degree of risk involved. However to minimize risk you would need to do some research and partner with a reliable real estate broker who can guide you to a profitable deal.', 'However if you are not familiar with the real estate market then buying apartments in under-construction new projects in Gurgaon. For one these real estate developers will have a sample flat ready that will give you an idea of the floor space and how the apartment would actually look once the project is complete.', 'Plot No.257-A Block  A 40 Feet Road', 'Sector  110 New Palam Vihar Phase-II', 'Gurgaon  122017', 'Phone: +91-124-2467403', 'www.lumbiniterracehomes.com / www.brisk.in ', 'Sector-109 Gurgaon-122017 ', 'T : +91 124 2467400/402 ', 'M: +91 8800896707 /08 /09 /10 ', ' E : ', 'info@brisk.in']
